{"ticker": "AKE", "company": "ARKEMA", "weight_sum": 0.13, "etfs": ["PRNT"], "is_private": false, "query": "($AKE OR \"Arkema\") -is:retweet min_faves:10 since:2026-04-28 until:2026-04-29", "n_fetched": 2, "n_kept": 2, "n_dropped": 0, "kept": [{"type": "tweet", "id": "2049154387323310085", "url": "https://x.com/instinctfoot/status/2049154387323310085", "twitterUrl": "https://twitter.com/instinctfoot/status/2049154387323310085", "text": "\ud83d\udea8Playoffs les dates et heures sont connues.\n\nLes demi-finales des playoffs d\u2019Arkema Premi\u00e8re Ligue se joueront le samedi 16 mai. \n\nL\u2019OL Lyonnes, d\u00e9j\u00e0 assur\u00e9 de terminer en t\u00eate du classement, disputera sa demi-finale au Groupama Stadium le samedi 16 mai \u00e0 18h. \n\nLa seconde affiche, programm\u00e9e \u00e0 21h, sera connue \u00e0 l\u2019issue de la J22, le 6 mai, dont le r\u00e9sultat d\u00e9terminera le club h\u00f4te de cette autre demi-finale.\n\n#footballfeminin #arkemapl", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "retweetCount": 8, "replyCount": 1, "likeCount": 24, "quoteCount": 2, "viewCount": 2405, "createdAt": "Tue Apr 28 15:50:52 +0000 2026", "lang": "fr", "bookmarkCount": 4, "isReply": false, "inReplyToId": null, "conversationId": "2049154387323310085", "displayTextRange": [0, 273], "inReplyToUserId": null, "inReplyToUsername": null, "author": {"type": "user", "userName": "instinctfoot", "url": "https://x.com/instinctfoot", "twitterUrl": "https://twitter.com/instinctfoot", "id": "876798176069656576", "name": "Instinct Foot & Sport", "isVerified": false, "isBlueVerified": true, "verifiedType": null, "profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2039392712999182336/Ql34C0KW_normal.jpg", "coverPicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_banners/876798176069656576/1758138268", "description": "\ud83d\uddde\ufe0f Le sport F\u00e9minin fait la Une \u26bd\ufe0f Arkema PL \u2022 CDF\u2022 UWCL \u2022 World Cup \u2022 Weuro \ud83d\udcca Infos \u2022 Stats \u2022 Analyses \ud83c\udf